# Smithian Fold Theory of Everything (SFTOE)

[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)
[![Python 3.9+](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.9+-green.svg)](https://python.org)
